quran[118]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,Meubahgia that ureueng meuiman
  23,2,Dalam seumbahyang khuchu‘ that leupah
  23,3,Han tom geupeubuet nyang sia-sia Buet deungon kata hana tom salah
  23,4,Geubri ngon zakeuet meu na hareuta
  23,5,Meunalee teuma geujaga leupah
  23,6,Meulengkan ubak peurumoh gopnyan Namiet teubosan teuma geuh nyang sah Meunyo nyan teuma han jeuet keu cupa
  23,7,Laen tamita nyankeuh nyang salah
  23,8,Bandum amanah ngon janji gopnyan Meubacut pih han sagai geuubah
  23,9,Lom geupeulahra seumbahyang gopnyan
  23,10,Nyankeuh ureueng nyan teurimong upah Geutueng pusaka upah ureueng nyan
  23,11,Pusaka gopnyan churuga indah Churuga Firdaus teumpat ureueng nyan Keukai di sinan gopnyan geukeubah
  23,12,Ka Kamoe peujeuet dum manusia Bak tanoh baja phon asai liah
  23,13,Lheueh nyan Meupeujeuet bak sititek ie Bak teumpat leupie sideh Meukeubah
  23,14,Te sititek nyan teuma Meupeujeuet Keu laen sipheuet saboh cak darah y Meupeujeuet darah teuma keu asoe Keunan Meupasoe tuleueng meugapah Meubalot tuleueng teuma ngon asoe Teuma ‘oh dudoe bandum Meuubah d Kamoe peujeuet jih makhluk laen Keubit that licen peuneujeuet Allah Maha Suci that Tuhan nyang peujeuet Hana soe peujeuet lagee nyan indah
  23,15,‘Oh Iheueh nyan teuma gata dum mate
  23,16,Neubangket teuh le teuma le Allah Uroe kiamat teuma geubangket Hana padum trep sang-sang that bagah
  23,17,Ka Kamoe peujeuet di ateueh gata Tujoh angkasa nyang raya leupah Hana tom lale teuma di-Kamoe Nyang meupeujeuet nyoe sabe meupapah
  23,18,Meupeutren ujeuen sideh di langet » Kada jih meuhat hana meupeugah i Kamoe peudong ie sinan di bumoe Teuma di-Kamoe ek lom meuruah Kamoe kuasa meupeuboh ie nyan
  23,19,Keu keubon teuh nyan teuma meukeubah Keubon keureuma anggor boh kayee Nyang laen teuntee dum le that leupah Boh kayee dum nyan mangat tapajoh
  23,20,Teuma na saboh kayee meutuah Kaycee nyan timoh di Thursina Minyeuk dum jibri bak kayee ceudah Teuma makanan tapajoh leumak
  23,21,Binatang teurnak pih saboh tuah le dalam pruet jih meubri keu gata Laen dum teuma le that phaedah Tapajoh sie jih mangat that rasa
  23,22,Tagiduek teuma jan tameulangkah Saban ngon kapai keu keundraan gata Bak rueng jih lanja taek le bagah
  23,23,Kamoe kirem Noh bak kaom gopnyan Geukheun le gopnyan kaom meutuah Taseumah Allah nyankeuh nyang Tuhan Tan laen Tuhan teuh meu kon Allah Pakon han gata tatem takwa
  23,24,Jiseuot sigra le kaphe jadah Awak nyang kaphe lam kaomgeuh nyoe Jikheun peue jih nyoe jikeumeung peugah ô Jih manusia cit lagee gata Napsu mulia jih tapeumeugah Napsu beuleubeh jih nibak gata Nyankeuh jijak ba haba beurakah Meunyo Neukheundak Tuhan Hadharat Cit malaikat Neukirem bagah Han tom tadeungo bak du-du tanyoe Haba lagee nyoe nyang jih jak peugah Han tom tadeungo bak ureueng dilee
  23,25,Bit jih ka seudee akai ka salah i Bit meunan tapreh cit meupadum trep
  23,26,Jikheun lon sulet wahe ya Allah Neutulong lon nyoe han jitem pateh Nabi Noh meuceh meunan neupeugah
  23,27,Kamoe bri wahyu teuma bak gopnyan Meunyo ka meunan tamita hilah Tapeugot kapai jinoe digata Jeuet Kamoe jaga mangat bek salah Ngon wahyu Kamoe meu ka troh watee Gata jak dilee Kamoe peuleupah Meu ka teupancar ie nibak dapu Watee nyan laju gata beukeumah Dua-dua peue meupasang-pasang Tayue ek rijang keunan beubagah Ngon ahli gata nyang seutot gata Nyankeuh nyang taba jan tameulangkah Meulengkan soe-soe nyang ka na kada Keu jih ceulaka Neubri le Allah Awak nyang lalem nyan bek talakee Karam dum teuntee lam laot luah Bek lakee bak Lon teuntang awak nyan
  23,28,Digata keunan taek le bagah Meu ka lheueh taek u dalam kapai Bek tuwo sagai tapujoe Allah Alhamdulillah Tuhan tapujoe Ban dumna kamoe ka Neupeuleupah Neupeuglah kamoe nibak si lalem
  23,29,Takheun lom laen wahe ya Allah Neupeuduek kamoe bak saboh teumpat Nyang ka beureukat nanggroe meutuah Droe-Neuh sineujroh ureueng bri teumpat
  23,30,Bandum nyan ayat kuasa Allah Bandum atra nyan Meubri cobaan
  23,31,Di likot jih nyan meugantoe bagah Meugantoe deungon kurun nyang laen
  23,32,Teuma meukirem lom Rasulullah Rasul Meukirem dalam kawan jih Geuyue dum bak jih taseumah Allah Tuhan nyang laen bandum kon tuhan Pakon gata han takwa keu Allah
  23,33,Jikheun le kaphe lam kaom gopnyan Awak nyan nyang han turot peurintah Uroe akhirat pih jikheun hana Lam udep donya kamoe bri mewah Jikheun dum jih nyoe pih manusia Saban ngon gata hana meuubah Peue nyang tapajoh ngon peue nyang tajep Jipajoh jijep pih saban leupah
  23,34,Meunyo taikot cit manusia Nyang sa ngon gata rogoe that leupah
  23,35,Peue jimeujanji jikheun bak gata ‘Oh mate gata jikheun geubalah ‘Oh jeuet keu tanoh teuh tinggai tuleueng Geubangketteuh lom meunan jipeugah
  23,36,Jioh that jioh nyang jijanji nyan
  23,37,Nyang beutoi kon nyan nyang hana sosah Udep lam donya mate ngon udep Hana le bangket tanyoe ka sudah
  23,38,Kon laen jih nyan jipeuna-peuna s Sulet lagoena jikheun keu Allah Gata nyoe han jeuet meuiman keu jih
  23,39,Pakri nyoe dum jih wahe ya Allah Neutulong lon nyoe han jitem pateh Rasul nyan meuceh meunan geupeugah
  23,40,Kheun Tuhan teuma han trep le sagai Jih nyan meunyeusai bandum jih teulah
  23,41,Bit jitak treuk jih dum le geulanteue Hana meusapeue jiteumee peugah f Lagee broh teuboh treuk jih dum sinan Kaom nyang lalem jioh that leupah
  23,42,Meugantoe treuk jih ngon kuron laen Di likot jih nyan Meugantoe bagah
  23,43,Beurangri ummat meu goh troh ajai Han jeuet peuawai meu ube seupah Meu ka troh ajai han jeuet peuakhe
  23,44,Kamoe kirem le Rasul lom bagah Meuturot-turot Meukirem Rasul Bandum nyan Rasul sulet jipeugah Bandum jih teuma Meupeubinasa Jeuet treuk jih haba dalam seujarah Jioh that kaom nyang hana iman
  23,45,Musa ‘oh lheueh nyan Kamoe yue langkah Musa ngon Harun Meukirem keunoe t Ngon ayat Kamoe geuba peurintah Muʻjizat nyata geujak ba keunan
  23,46,Ubak Peuraʻeun kaphe seurakah k Teuma teukabo jih ngon kaom jih Mbong that bandum jih hana ban peugah
  23,47,Jikheun peue kamoe meujak meuiman Keu dua insan lagee nyan rendah Bandua jih nyan saban ngon tanyoe Kaom jih tanyoe bandum jiseumah
  23,48,Han jitem pateh bandua gopnyan Jeuet treuk awak nyan binasa sudah
  23,49,Cit ka Kamoe bri kitab keu Musa Kadang cit ek na keu jih hidayah Kadang Neutunyok dum jih le Tuhan
  23,50,Aneuk Maryam teuma meutuah Aneuk Maryam deungon ma gopnyan Tanda bak gopnyan Kamoe peuleumah Kamoe bri teumpat gopnyan bandua Bak tanoh data geupiyoh payah Teumpat nyang teunang saboh geurugoh Sinan geupiyoh ie pih na mudah
  23,51,Hai Rasul-Rasul pajoh le gata Makanan gata nyang jroh-jroh leupah Lom pih tapubuet dum buet nyang got-got Peue nyang tapubuet Lon teupeue bagah
  23,52,Nyan ummat gata cit saboh bandum Lon Po gata dum nyang beu taseumah Teuma takwa gata dum keu Lon
  23,53,Peucah treuk jih dum meupisah-pisah Bandum jih galak keu peureute droe
  23,54,Bah meunan keudroe jih bek tapapah Bah sisat jih dum dang-dang troh watee Meu ka troh watee abeh jih sudah
  23,55,Peue jisangka dum Kamoe bri keu jih Le that aneuk jih hareuta mewah
  23,56,Meupeubagah jih bak keubajikan Jiteupeue pih tan dijih ka salah
  23,57,Ureueng nyang takot dum keu Po gopnyan
  23,58,Lom geumeuiman keu ayat Allah
  23,59,Keu Po gopnyan han geupeucharikat
  23,60,Ureueng meularat geubri seudeukah Ureueng nyan geubri peue-peue nyang geubri Teumakot ate gopnyan keu Allah Teumakot gopnyan geuwoe bak Tuhan
  23,61,Nyankeuh ureueng nyan nyang got that bagah Meudilee-dilee gopnyan bak buet got
  23,62,Hana Meupeubrat teuma bek salah Di-Kamoe Meuyue nyang ek geupeubuet Hana Meuyue buet nyang leupah-leupah Lam kitab Kamoe narit nyang beuna Hana elanya meu ube seupah Jih nyan pih bandum han geuelanya
  23,63,Ate jih teuma nyang sisat leupah Hana jipike dijih atra nyoe Laen nibak nyoe pih buet jih salah Buet nyang hana got bandum jipeubuet
  23,64,Baro teukeujot ‘oh jieu balah ë Jieu geuazeueb awak nyang chik-chik Meu jigeumeuciek treuk riyoh leupah
  23,65,Bek kageumeuciek le dum uroe nyoe Hana troh keu noe soe jak tulong kah
  23,66,Watee geubaca dilee ayat Lon Keu kah han katueng kasurot bagah
  23,67,Ngon mbong kah kakheun dum macam-macam ‘Oh watee malam kapeugah-peugah
  23,68,Peue tan jipike narit nyang jikheun Bak du-du jih kon ka lheueh geupeugah Atawa du-du jih dilee awai Goh lom troh sagai geuba peurintah
  23,69,Peue han jituri Rasul jih nyan dum Jeuet jiungki dum peue nyan geupeugah
  23,70,Atawa jikheun gopnyan ka gila Tapi nyang geuba keubit risalah Haba nyang beuna geuba ubak jih Teuma le that jih beunci jih leupah Le that jih beunci keu peue nyang beuna
  23,71,Peuturot hawa dijih nyang salah Meunyo napsu jih nyan tapeuturot Abeh dum karot peuneujeuet Allah Tatinggai nyang hak taturot jih nyoe Langet ngon bumoe abeh dum cah prah Ngon bandum ureueng nyang na di sinan Rusak bandum nyan hana ban peugah Kamoe bri ayat peuingat keu jih Jipaleng dijih hana jipapah
  23,72,Atawa peue na talakee bak jih C Beujibri le jih keu gata upah Upah Po gata nyan nyang leubeh got Tan laen nyang got meu kon bri Allah Tuhan Sineujroh nyang bri raseuki
  23,73,Tahei jih lagi bak jalan Allah Jalan nyang beutoi jalan nyang teupat
  23,74,Dikaphe meuhat jalan jih salah Han jipateh na uroe akhirat Jalan nyang teupat dijih jikeubah
  23,75,Meunyo Meusayang le Kamoe keu jih j Meupeuleupah jih dum han le sosah Teuntee jimeuʻen lam darohaka Hana le reuda jipeubuet salah
  23,76,Ka lheueh Kamoe bri roe azeueb keu jih Han cit jitem jih turot peurintah Han jitem teukui keudeh keu Po jih
  23,77,Meubri treuk keu jih azeueb that leupah Meujeuet treuk jih nyan dum putoh asa ‘Oh pinto seksa ka Kamoe peuhah
  23,78,Tuhan nyang peujeuet geulunyueng mata Ngon ate gata carong ngon ceudah Tapi nit gata nyang tatem chukor
  23,79,Neubri gata le di bumoe Allah Meuaneuk cucoteuh dum di bumoe Meusapat dudoe teuma bak Allah
  23,80,Tuhan peuhudep Tuhan peumate Malam teuka le uroe pih leupah Malam ngon uroe cit meungkleh sabe Hankeuh tapike ngon akai ceudah
  23,81,Tapi kheunjih sa ngon ureueng jameun Saban ngon jih kheun hana meuubah
  23,82,Jikheun peue keubit ‘oh mate tanyoe Geubangket tanyoe teuma geupeugah p *Oh jeuet keu tanoh teuh tinggai tuleueng Geubangket teuh lom mustahe leupah
  23,83,Keubit geutanyoe ngon du-du tanyoe Geujanji meunoe dilee ka sudah Atranyoe dongeng ureueng nyang dilee Bandum meuteuntee haba beurakah
  23,84,Takheun soe nyang po bumoe ngon asoe Bandum sinaroe tacuba peugah Meunyo tateupeue takheun soe po jih
  23,85,Teuntee seuotjih nyang po nyan Allah Takheun boh pakon cit han taingat
  23,86,Takheun po langet soe lom ci peugah Po langet tujoh po ‘arasy raya
  23,87,Jiseuot lanja po jih nyan Allah Takheun boh pakon han tatakwa
  23,88,Takheun soe raja lom taci peugah Nyang po keurajeuen seugala rupa Nyang ek neubela soe-soe nyang sosah Beurangsoe laen han ek jibela Meunyo neuseksa soe nyan ci peugah Meunyo tateupeue takheun soe dih nyan
  23,89,Teuntee jikheun nyan cit sidroe Allah Takheun peue cit ek gata jitaki
  23,90,Tapi ka Meubri keu jih dum sudah Atra nyang beuna ka lheueh Kamoe bri Droe jih nyang taki sulet that leupah
  23,91,Hana aneuk-Neuh sagai di Tuhan Tan laen tuhan sajan ngon Allah Sabab meunyo na tuhan nyang laen r Makhluk laen geupeujeuet sudah Meuseunoh-seunoh peugot atra droe 3 Ka keuh rayek droe bandum geupeugah Maha Suci that Allah lagee nyan
  23,92,Nyang keubit Tuhan cit sidroe Allah Nyang han deuh taeu got nyang deuh taeu Bandum deuh Neueu meunyo le Allah Bandum deuh Neueu Maha manyang that Nibak charikat lagee jih peugah
  23,93,Takheun Tuhanku meunyo Neumeung bri Peue nyang Neujanji Neumeung peuleumah Neumeung peukalon atra nyan bak lon
  23,94,Tuhanku bek lon roh lam beurakah Bek roh lon dalam kaom nyang lalem
  23,95,Meunyo Kamoe tem ek Meupeuleumah Ek Meupeukalon dum nyan bak gata
  23,96,Teuma digata beugot tapapah Tatulak ngon got buet nyang brok jih nyan Kamoe teupeue nyan peue nyang jipeugah
  23,97,Takheun Tuhanku Neupeulindong lon Nibak s‘ah chetan jiyue buet salah
  23,98,Neupeulindong lon wahe Tuhanku Bek jipeukaru bak lon jilangkah
  23,99,Teuma awak nyan ‘oh teuka mawot Han ek le meumot jikheun treuk bagah Tuhanku Neubri lon woe u donya
  23,100,Lon peubuet teuma amai jroh leupah Amai nyang shaleh nyang tinggai dilee Jinoe meuteuntee han le lon keubah Tapi atra nyan narit jih mantong Di likot jih dong padang that luah Sampoe geubangket jih han troh teuka
  23,101,‘Oh Sangkai kala pih geuyup sudah Uroe nyan han le geutanyong bangsa Han le chedara nyang meugah-meugah Han jeuet teumanyong le bak uroe nyan
  23,102,Nyang brat timbangan nyan nyang meutuah Nyankeuh ureueng nyan nyang meubahgia
  23,103,Nyang phui ceulaka rugoe sileupah Jipeurugoe droe roh lam nuraka Keukai jeuep masa lam apui mirah
  23,104,Jisama muža jitot le apui Meugasui-gasui hanco ngon patah b i
  23,105,Kon ka geubaca dilee ayat Lon Keu gata bandum sulet tapeugah
  23,106,Kheun treuk awak nyan hai Tuhan kamoe Jigiduek kamoe le buet nyang salah £ Kakeuh meunang jih u ateueh kamoe Jeuet treuk dum kamoe sisat sileupah
  23,107,Neubri meuteubiet nibak teumpat nyoe Hai Tuhan kamoe saket that leupah Meunyo kamoe woe buet lagee dilee H Nyan ka meuteuntee kamoe nyang salah Kamoe nyang lalem droe meuelanya
  23,108,Neukheun bah hinakeuh sinan dikah Beujrakeuh sinan mangat karasa Bek le meuhaba ngon Lon nyoe dikah
  23,109,Saboh jamaʻah nibak hamba Lon Ureueng nyan geukheun wahe ya Allah Wahe Po kamoe kamoe meuiman Neuampon teuma kamoe ka salah Droe-Neuh sineujroh ureueng geumaseh Kamoe Neugaseh wahe ya Allah
  23,110,Kaulok-ulok ureueng nyan bandum Hingga jeuet keu Lon tuwokeuh dikah f Bandumkeuh tuwo kaingat keu Lon Dawok kapeukhem ureueng nyan dikah
  23,111,Uroe nyoe gopnyan nyang meubahgia k Sabab geusaba jinoe Lon balah
  23,112,Neukheun padum thon keuh dalam bumoe
  23,113,Sang-sang siuroe jiseuot bagah Meukon siuroe sang sikhan uroe Tatanyong keudroe bak ureueng ceudah Keudeh bak ureueng nyang jeuet meubileueng
  23,114,Sideh kah geukheun rijang sileupah Meunyo kateupeue sideh kah tinggai Cit siat sagai leupah that bagah
  23,115,Peue bak tasangka Meupeujeuet gata Cit sia-sia hana phaedah p Hana geupeuwoe gata le bak Lon
  23,116,Maha Suci Lon Raja nyang meugah Raja nyang beuna nyang mat keurajeuen Kon laen tuhan meulengkan Allah Allahkeuh nyang Po ‘arasy mulia
  23,117,Soe nyang tapuja meunyo kon Allah Beurangsoe puja tuhan nyang laen Jikheun na laen sajan ngon Allah Hana meudali nyang jipeugah nyan Neukira dum nyan teuma le Allah Tuhan nyang Po jih peugot keunira Hana bahgia si kaphe jadah
  23,118,Takheun Tuhanku beu-Neupeuampon Neugaseh keu lon ureueng nyang salah Droe-Neuh sineujroh ureueng geumaseh Bandum Neugaseh wahe ya Allah AN-NUR (CAHAYA) s Ngon nama Allah lon peuphon surat Tuhan Hadharat nyang Maha Murah Tuhanku Sidroe geumaseh that-that Donya akhirat rahmat Neulimpah